descriptionHtml:
Imposter Sort Puzzle 1 is a cute, fun, and relaxing puzzle game.
It is totally offline and really friendly to everyone.
It is lightweight to install but its graphics and motions are decent.
Try it now, you won't regret it!

Imposter Sort Puzzle 1: Cute, Fun and Relaxing is easy to play but sometimes really challenging.
You can also relax or train your brain with this puzzle game.

How to play:
Sort the imposters and sort them by colors.
An ultimate imposter or a crewmate will be summoned with 4 main parts.
Get through the challenge by summoning all imposters in the cabin.
The imposters will be revealed after they are all summoned.

creator: INDIEZ GLOBAL PTE. LTD.
descriptionHtml:
Impostor Sort Puzzle is a fun and addictive puzzle game! Try to sort the colored impostor in the cabins until all imposters with the same color stay in the same cabins. A challenging yet relaxing game to exercise your brain!

★ HOW TO PLAY:
• Tap any cabin to move the impostor lie on top in the cabin to another one.
• The rule is that you can only move a impostor on top of another impostor if both of them have the same color and the cabin you want to move into has enough space.
• Try not to get stuck - but don’t worry, you can always restart the level at any time.

★ FEATURES:
• One finger control.
• FREE & EASY TO PLAY.
• NO penalty & time limit; you can enjoy Impostor Sort Puzzle at your own pace!
